@startuml
hide circle
hide methods
hide stereotypes

skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam defaultFontName Segoe UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowColor #5B7083
skinparam ArrowThickness 1
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentBorderColor #6E879D
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 42
skinparam ranksep 46

title Diseño resumido de componentes del backend de TrackHabit Loop

top to bottom direction

component "Bootstrap e\ninfraestructura\nserver.ts, app.ts, db.ts" as be_boot
component "Configuración\nconfig.ts y entorno" as be_config
component "API Express" as be_api
component "Middleware\ntransversal" as be_mw
component "Módulo Auth / Users" as be_account
component "Módulo Habits /\nNutrition" as be_tracking
component "Módulo\nNotifications" as be_notif
component "Módulo Support /\nAppInfo" as be_support
component "Shared DTOs\npackages/shared" as be_shared
database "PostgreSQL" as be_pg

be_boot --> be_config
be_boot --> be_api
be_boot --> be_pg

be_api --> be_mw
be_api --> be_account
be_api --> be_tracking
be_api --> be_notif
be_api --> be_support

be_account ..> be_notif
be_tracking ..> be_notif

be_account ..> be_shared
be_notif ..> be_shared
be_support ..> be_shared

be_account --> be_pg
be_tracking --> be_pg
be_notif --> be_pg
be_support --> be_pg

be_boot -[hidden]down-> be_api
be_api -[hidden]down-> be_account
be_account -[hidden]right-> be_tracking
be_tracking -[hidden]right-> be_notif
be_notif -[hidden]right-> be_support
be_support -[hidden]right-> be_shared
be_shared -[hidden]down-> be_pg

@enduml
